		<div class="title">
			<h4><a rel="nofollow" id="comment_link_64796653" name="comment_link_64796653" href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23458733&amp;cid=64796653" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64796653)" >Advertising != washing anything</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64796653" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64796653); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>3</a>, Insightful)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a rel="nofollow" href="//slashdot.org/~thegarbz">thegarbz</a>  <span class="uid"><a rel="nofollow" href="//slashdot.org/~thegarbz">( 1787294 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64796653">		
		on Wednesday September 18, 2024 @01:11PM (<span class="ind"></span><a rel="nofollow" href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23458733&amp;cid=64796653">#64796653</a>)
		<small> </small>
